reset
set default element hex
create surface rectangle width 1000 zplane
webcut body 1 with plane yplane offset 0
webcut body 1 with plane xplane offset 0
delete Surface 3
imprint all
merge all
compress all
curve 1 2 3 size 10
curve 4 5 6 7 size 50
curve all scheme equal
mesh curve all

surface all submap smooth off
surface all scheme submap
mesh surface all

create material 1
modify material 1 name 'TestMat'
modify material 1 set property 'MODULUS' value 1.68592e+10
modify material 1 set property 'POISSON' value 0.283744
modify material 1 set property 'DENSITY' value 1935.6
modify material 1 set property 'BIOT_ALPHA' value 1

set duplicate block elements off
block 1 add surface 1 2 
block 1  material 1 cs 1 category plane order 6

create force on vertex 5 force value 1  direction 0 1 0
bcdep force 1 value 'ricker(1e+10, 30, 0, time)'

create absorption on curve 4 7 1 2 

analysis type dynamic elasticity dim2 planestrain preload off
dynamic method full_solution scheme explicit maxsteps 100000 maxtime 0.3
dynamic results everytime 0.01
output nodalforce off energy off record3d off material on without_smoothing off fullperiodic off

